Package org.js4ms.amt.gateway

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AmtDatagramSource
    A MessageSource that constructs an AMT multicast endpoint to forward datagrams sent to a specific port and one or more any-source or source-specific addresses.
    AmtIPInterface  
    AmtIPInterfaceManager  
    AmtMulticastEndpoint
    A MulticastEndpoint that uses AMT to request and receive multicast datagrams sent to a specific multicast group address and UDP port number.
    AmtPseudoInterface
    An AMT pseudo-interface.
    AmtPseudoInterfaceManager
    Constructs and manages a collection of AmtPseudoInterface objects.

    AmtUDPInterfaceManager
